cc:Work.dc:title: Box - Keypad
cc:Work.dc:description:
Generator for keypads with mechanical switches.
Note that top layers use a different material thickness according to the top1_thickness and top2_thickness (if enabled).
Created with Boxes.py (https://festi.info/boxes.py) Command line: boxes Keypad --FingerJoint_angle=90.0 --FingerJoint_style=rectangular --FingerJoint_surroundingspaces=1.0 --FingerJoint_edge_width=1.0 --FingerJoint_extra_length=0.0 --FingerJoint_finger=2.0 --FingerJoint_play=0.0 --FingerJoint_space=2.0 --FingerJoint_width=1.0 --h=30 --top1_thickness=4 --top2_enable=0 --top2_thickness=1.5 --pcb_mount_enable=0 --pcb_mount_enable=1 --led_enable=0 --diode_enable=0 --cutout_type=castle --columns_definition=2x5 --thickness=3.0 --format=svg --tabs=0.0 --debug=0 --labels=0 --labels=1 --reference=100 --inner_corners=loop --burn=0.04 Url: http://festi.info/Keypad?FingerJoint_angle=90.0&FingerJoint_style=rectangular&FingerJoint_surroundingspaces=1.0&FingerJoint_edge_width=1.0&FingerJoint_extra_length=0.0&FingerJoint_finger=2.0&FingerJoint_play=0.0&FingerJoint_space=2.0&FingerJoint_width=1.0&h=30&top1_thickness=4&top2_enable=0&top2_thickness=1.5&pcb_mount_enable=0&pcb_mount_enable=1&led_enable=0&diode_enable=0&cutout_type=castle&columns_definition=2x5&thickness=3.0&format=svg&tabs=0.0&debug=0&labels=0&labels=1&reference=100&inner_corners=loop&burn=0.04&render=1 SettingsUrl: http://festi.info/Keypad?FingerJoint_angle=90.0&FingerJoint_style=rectangular&FingerJoint_surroundingspaces=1.0&FingerJoint_edge_width=1.0&FingerJoint_extra_length=0.0&FingerJoint_finger=2.0&FingerJoint_play=0.0&FingerJoint_space=2.0&FingerJoint_width=1.0&h=30&top1_thickness=4&top2_enable=0&top2_thickness=1.5&pcb_mount_enable=0&pcb_mount_enable=1&led_enable=0&diode_enable=0&cutout_type=castle&columns_definition=2x5&thickness=3.0&format=svg&tabs=0.0&debug=0&labels=0&labels=1&reference=100&inner_corners=loop&burn=0.04
